OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will
OL,6,Fremain mostly cloudy with some showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain, heavy at times,
OL,8,Falong with some drier periods. A very
OL,9,Fmild, rather humid night with a
OL,10,Ffreshening southerly breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FAnother cloudy day with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain, some of which will
OL,14,Fbe heavy especially ove the Southwest.
OL,15,FSome drier spells too.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,18,Fclears north Saturday morning to leave
OL,19,Fthe afternoon and Sunday dry and
OL,20,Fbright, and becoming warm. Monday
OL,21,Fstaying dry with some sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
